## ğŸ¯ Project Objectives
1. Build an image classification model to categorize images.
2. Implement an object detection system to locate objects within images.
3. Integrate **Text-to-Speech (TTS)** to enhance accessibility for visually impaired users.
4. Evaluate the performance using standard metrics like accuracy, precision, and recall.
5. Create a user-friendly interface for testing and visualizing results.

